text: The entire soundtrack, or at least most of it, is taken from an album named Krater by Christian Gabel. Both that album and the game are inspired by a series of, what looks like, storyboards for a movie set in post-apocalyptic Sweden that Gabel bought at a flea market. (If I remember the story correctly)
